2D Graphics: Basic Concepts, 2D Graphics on OpenGL, Algorithms for rasterization, clipping, filling, etc. 3D Graphics: Basic Concepts, 3D Graphics on OpenGL, Viewing and Projection, Hierarchical Modelling. Visible Surface Determination: Z-buffer Algorithm, BSP-Tree, Visible Ray Tracing. Appearance: Intensity and Colours, Colour Models. Lighting and Shading: Shading Models, Simulating Realism, Shadows, Transparency. Represention: Curves, Surfaces etc. Ray Tracing: Visibility & Shading.
